        <name>init_platform</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Initializes the platform hardware and enables necessary features. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function performs platform-specific initialization steps required before running the main application. It optionally calls ps7_init() for Zynq platforms if running outside of the SDK, enables instruction and data caches, and initializes the UART for standard output.</para><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>For Zynq: Optionally calls ps7_init() if needed (see comments).</para></listitem><listitem><para>Enables processor caches.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Initializes UART for console output. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
